      "description": "Set attachment conditions for the specified link directions. The current attachment condition will be replaced by the condition specified here. Conditions are specified in keyword pairs, the first (keyword) being the degree-of-freedom and the second ([linkattachoptions]) being the type of condition to use. The following keywords are available to specify the degree-of-freedom:",
      "keywords": [
